snippet.title: Ermii Kart Ds Legacy Edition - All 32 Custom Tracks & 6 Custom Battle Tracks
snippet.description:
Ermii Kart Ds is a rom hack for Mario Kart Ds that features 32 custom race tracks, 6 custom battle tracks, new characters (And selectable alternate skins and characters), custom karts and much more made by Emelber.

You can download Ermii Kart Ds Legacy Edition here: https://youtu.be/8_AuFruqk5E

Here are all of the custom tracks tracks in the game, including the 16 custom Nitro Courses and the 16 custom Retro Courses, as well as the 6 custom Battle Tracks.

A showcase of all custom characters, costumes and karts can be found here: https://youtu.be/or3aUV_ctZA

This was played and record on a Samsung Galaxy S9+ using the DraStic Ds Emulator on Android
